Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.30,0:01:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎少爺…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.58,0:02:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.48,0:02:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十話\N真古流的復活！\N呼風喚雨終極之殺人劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.13,0:02:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我用這雙眼睛看到了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.53,0:02:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個男人被傳說的理由了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.13,0:02:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 這堻ㄛO急流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.10,0:03:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙已經回不來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.90,0:03:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了 拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.30,0:03:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.04,0:03:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍哥還沒回來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.51,0:03:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候\N如果我跟劍心一起去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.72,0:03:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是劍哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.13,0:03:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.40,0:04:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.23,0:04:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生了什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.63,0:04:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠小姐…由太郎少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.07,0:04:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這孩子 好燙喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.11,0:04:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掉到海 溺水了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.71,0:04:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直昏迷不醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.28,0:04:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.61,0:04:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.82,0:04:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.88,0:04:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這麼濕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.39,0:04:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.75,0:04:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓各位擔心真是對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.39,0:04:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底發生了什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.39,0:04:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連你都這樣了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.53,0:04:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.30,0:04:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管發生了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.60,0:04:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎和小薰小姐\N都由我來保護…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.91,0:04:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只會擔心別人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.01,0:04:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了別人可以不要自己的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.71,0:04:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心真是笨蛋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就快要跟政府戰鬥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.52,0:05:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個大房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.53,0:05:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將成為我們的城堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.30,0:05:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底要開始什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.66,0:05:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些人到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.70,0:05:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎少爺\N已經全部都交給雷十太大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.00,0:05:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.61,0:05:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是少爺現在到哪堨h了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.71,0:05:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請告訴我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.38,0:05:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.21,0:05:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太囉嗦了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.45,0:06:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小少爺現在很安全…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.62,0:06:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位先暫時離開這大房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.09,0:06:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村先生一定會救我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.06,0:06:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好嗎 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.27,0:06:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍術是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.53,0:06:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟被殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.54,0:06:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩者合而為一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.04,0:06:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從現在開始你是我們的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.35,0:06:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經不是小孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.91,0:07:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真古流的傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.48,0:07:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在維新後不久已經在流傳著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.92,0:07:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從那時候起政府也注意到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.35,0:07:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是毫無道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.22,0:07:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人劍登峰造極的劍客們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.26,0:07:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要建設國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.03,0:07:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能丟棄劍的武士的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.83,0:07:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以小生來說是可以理解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.13,0:07:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是總覺得要流很多血的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.94,0:07:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不去說服一下的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.21,0:07:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.07,0:07:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經受傷了 你還在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.21,0:07:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊 而且他們並不是說了\N就能明白的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.21,0:07:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的缺點是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.58,0:07:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.65,0:07:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一個人就能背負所有的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.19,0:07:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你忘了有我存在這可不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.59,0:07:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.09,0:07:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.06,0:07:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什..什麼嘛 不要笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.33,0:08:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位 這堛漲W產是溫泉饅頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.37,0:08:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請吃看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.97,0:08:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饅頭 我要吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.54,0:08:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惠姐跟小綾小雀到哪堨h了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.24,0:08:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她們出去採藥草了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.05,0:08:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要一次就塞進嘴巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.32,0:08:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.42,0:08:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.32,0:08:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎 你醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.22,0:08:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臉色已經好很多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.76,0:08:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這堿O你的家嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.56,0:08:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是..是.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為某些原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.30,0:08:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望由太郎少爺暫時住在這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.80,0:08:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.20,0:08:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是你救我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.90,0:08:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.87,0:08:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要回到雷十太師父那堙I
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.18,0:08:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 你這不知好歹的混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.98,0:08:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.08,0:08:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正想趕你出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.38,0:08:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是劍心說\N不要讓你再回去雷十太的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.06,0:08:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竹刀只是玩具而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.96,0:08:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷十太師父說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.86,0:09:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有真的日本刀\N才能有優越的靈魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.43,0:09:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷十太..師父嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.77,0:09:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師父是我的理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.47,0:09:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.01,0:09:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.34,0:09:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要走的話\N用那支日本刀把我打倒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.25,0:09:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.38,0:09:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來分勝負吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.89,0:09:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.59,0:09:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是真的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.99,0:09:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死了也可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.10,0:09:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.31,0:09:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.28,0:09:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷十太教你的\N好像是輸的那方面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.55,0:09:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,…囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.72,0:10:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.53,0:10:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要偷逃出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.53,0:10:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真要出去的話\N就堂堂正正的打敗我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.13,0:10:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.74,0:10:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下..我還沒輸呢.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.04,0:10:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.41,0:10:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人從輸中才會長大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.14,0:10:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要碰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.88,0:10:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輸了也不是沒有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.48,0:10:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷十太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.72,0:10:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從來沒教過由太郎少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.69,0:10:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會知道這個的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.89,0:10:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要練習看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.89,0:10:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神谷活心流的練習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.60,0:10:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神谷…活心流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.73,0:10:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看了你後就覺得技癢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.24,0:10:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能引以為榮真正的劍術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.91,0:10:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以從心理開始陷進去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.67,0:10:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個練習…可以成為強者嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.88,0:10:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會成為強者的…一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 幫我練習吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.42,0:11:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三天以內我一定要勝了那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.19,0:11:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.62,0:11:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是泡澡的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.03,0:11:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定不逃走要打倒你為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.53,0:11:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後再正大光明的\N從這個家堥咱X去給你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓他看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.51,0:11:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始練習攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.98,0:11:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種動作很簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.85,0:11:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.59,0:11:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 完全不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.69,0:11:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 哪堣ㄕ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.76,0:11:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.79,0:11:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神谷活心流是保護人的劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保護…人的劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.86,0:11:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 只要有保護心愛人的心\N就會成為力量的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.90,0:11:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心愛的人…
