Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.09,0:16:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是劍心比雷十太還要好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.12,0:16:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那又另當別論了
